      "name": "Makourai, the Lightning Strike",
      "effect": "(This card is always treated as an \"Archfiend\" card.)\nTarget 1 \"Archfiend\" monster you control; it gains 600 ATK, then you can destroy all monsters your opponent controls with lower original ATK than that monster's ATK. During your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 Level 6 Fiend monster with 2500 ATK in your GY; add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of \"Makourai, the Lightning Strike\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
